03/02/82  forum request:  forum_dir, fd

Syntax:  fd


Syntax as an active request:  [fd]


Function: 
Prints/returns the absolute pathname of the central forum directory.


Notes:
The central forum directory is the location for site-approved public
forum forums. This directory is included in the default forum
search path. The forum request

   e add_search_paths forum [forum_dir]

may be used to add the central directory to the forum search path.
